--- Step 1: Create the New Private S3 Bucket:-

aws s3 mb s3://xfusion-sync-17951

By default, new buckets are private. You can explicitly block public access for extra safety:

aws s3api put-public-access-block \
  --bucket xfusion-sync-17951 \
  --public-access-block-configuration '{
    "BlockPublicAcls": true,
    "IgnorePublicAcls": true,
    "BlockPublicPolicy": true,
    "RestrictPublicBuckets": true
  }'



--- Step 2: Migrate Data from the Existing Bucket:-

aws s3 sync s3://xfusion-s3-5402 s3://xfusion-sync-17951



--- Step 3: Verify Data Consistency:-

-> List objects in both buckets:

aws s3 ls s3://xfusion-s3-5402 --recursive > source_list.txt
aws s3 ls s3://xfusion-sync-17951 --recursive > target_list.txt

-> Compare the lists:

diff source_list.txt target_list.txt
